{"tid":1611571,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聽到有黨鐵高級職員討論黨鐡近況","createTime":"2019-10-02T03:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T08:22:34.000Z","uid":302680,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"92ab9019d7f49083be50d7273e30edde2c4150cc","tid":1611571,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:54:53.000Z","msg":"大慨內容係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第一，所有針對黨鐵既行動，以爆玻璃既成本最高，維修成本高加上行政程序多，佢哋兒家剩餘資金主要係全部拎晒做維修</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">以後都要針對玻璃！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第二，最近黨鐡新請左大量保安，佢哋時薪為120蚊一個鐘，八個鐘一更</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">第三，佢哋對之前有單車跌落東鐵路軌好驚訝，因為好有機會影響高壓電</span>"},{"pid":"5d83b696ac2f007c786b8003081f4c58f46314c4","tid":1611571,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:55:03.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eb88f8b226557ded7cc55e69295d58d6a7a4c1bb","tid":1611571,"uid":302680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7c2450bbdb3d31263c79097310142b0d8a83a785","tid":1611571,"uid":267909,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T03:59:23.000Z","msg":"真？幫推一下，但我見依家好多無事閘機都蓋住？<br />\n怕以後唔夠閘機用？"},{"pid":"7bbfb98cc2507894116196f7b210de8d4b80a744","tid":1611571,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:07:03.000Z","msg":"製造就業機會 還富於民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87bb1c9b48fa5844891e3f8f7276ea29d28e1966","tid":1611571,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T04:07:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocki